branchCategory.name: C(D)S1*N, Air Cylinder, Double Acting, Single Rod, Non-lube Type
branchCategory.description: <p>Series CS1 air cylinder single rod double acting version of SMC's largest bore cylinder. This version is NOT pre-lubricated so a lubricator in your system is required. This series is available in bore sizes up to 300mm and stroke lengths up to 2400mm. Additionally, the CS1 can be ordered auto-switch capable. Other options include, large bore sizes up to 300mm, various mounting configurations, cushion for noise damping.</p>
